dct_description_sm: dressé par le P.H. Vincent ; gravé et imprimé par Erhard Fres.
Relief shown by shading and pictorially.
Coordinates approximate and based on Greenwich meridian.
Shows topography, drainage, boundaries, roads and travel routes, places of historical interest.
